上班的高管，很多人住在东莞常平，茶山等高级社区，坐和谐号上下班，很正常。深圳市区的房价比东莞常平茶山高出六七倍，1000 万的房子，在茶山常平最多 150 万到 200 万。一天车费也就 200 到 300 块，扣除假日，一个月也就 5000，一年最多 6 万，20 年最多 120 万。而且在市区上班，同样拥挤堵车，花费在路上的时间几乎相等。 你怎么看待跨省上班的这种现象呢？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-71a9f70a00fe6f1a151cce8bcc7f488d_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/472011106"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I9b+2kpu36LxaEAMaCDY3MTcwOTgzIOzEtYcGMHQ4iBhAJXIJNDcyMDExMTA2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "38_1626419166.44212", "card_id": "Q_472321006", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 119}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "NBA 总决赛 G4 布克和保罗基本无交流，你怎么看？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-638579548b633e02fca830bc6c508e70_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "52 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/472321006"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I9b+2kpu36LxaEAMaCDY3MjM5NjM3IM2wvocGMAc48wFAJnIJNDcyMzIxMDA2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "39_1626419166.4425185", "card_id": "Q_471039377", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 211}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么 86 版《西游记》严重脱离原著却没有妨碍这部剧成为经典？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "读了《西游记》原著之后，才知道 86 版电视剧《西游记》严重脱离了原著。 但是这并没有妨碍这部剧成为电视剧中的经典之作。 这是为什么呢？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-a7ba2ca19eb4b6a1becdb9a453a42620_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "49 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/471039377"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I9b+2kpu36LxaEAMaCDY2OTU0OTEwIPatnocGMCw4tQVAJ3IJNDcxMDM5Mzc3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_li